112
00:07:25.749 --> 00:07:27.055
Morning. Blaine.
Ooh. donuts.

113
00:07:27.229 --> 00:07:28.404
- Hey. Old-fashioned?
- Okay. Well. so.

114
00:07:28.578 --> 00:07:30.101
Carl keeps parking
his Goddamn--

115
00:07:30.275 --> 00:07:31.451
-Carl's his neighbor.
- My neighbor keeps

116
00:07:31.625 --> 00:07:32.669
