241
00:14:41.184 --> 00:14:43.012
Maybe we should
go for a walk. hey?

242
00:14:43.186 --> 00:14:44.840
- Okay! I'm going!
- Huh. Clayton? Okay.

243
00:14:45.014 --> 00:14:46.494
